Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory188.png'}
{3: 'Right when you are about to lose your patience, Camu finally contacts you.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Camu', 3: 'I found the control room. The connection underground is very unstable. I just found a place where I have signal.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Asimov', 3: "Good. 【kuroname】, transfer the visuals over. I'll run the analysis right away.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Camu', 3: "Hey, tech guy, hurry up. This place ain't all flowers and daisies even for me.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Asimov', 3: "Don't rush me. The more you rush, the slower it gets.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory194.png'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: "Ahem... That's basically what happened.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'There was a trip-up due to unexpected company, but the situation is still under our control.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'So where is our main dish?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'He is now wandering in the center of the auto-building structure. It will take him quite a while to squirm out of that place.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Long enough that the others can get our plans on the surface sorted out.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "Please do not worry, Miss Luna. He can't do anything in this hunting ground of ours.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'Of course, you need only will it, and I can arrange for the Corrupted to dispose of him—in advance, to prevent future problems.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'He, and the data he holds, will pose no threat to you, milady.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'No. Act according to plan.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'I decide what to do with him. Not you.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Roland, do you find my decision disagreeable?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: '...No. I would never.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory192.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: 'Hm-hmm... Miss Luna, the deeper you hide your true purpose, the greater my curiosity grows.', 4: '1'}
{1: 'AniZhuanchangBegin'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory188.png'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Scan complete.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Looks like this panel is linked to the passages in various parts of the park.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Asimov', 3: "As for the other one... It's probably the park's power management switch. Still looking into it.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Asimov', 3: "You might want to get a move on. Pressing the wrong button shouldn't be that much trouble. I'll contact you when I make progress.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Then the only thing that's left, is...", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Camu', 3: "【kuroname】, I'll just press all the buttons and pull all the levers. The floor's yours after that.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory191.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vera', 3: 'A theme park, huh... Just not a Vera place.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "But, good enough as long as there's a battlefield for me to dance. Nothing else matters.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'No. 21', 3: 'Ready. Awaiting orders.'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: "Yeah, yeah, ready since time immemorial. Y'know them ravens and hawks seem to be in the same mission area. You sure that's okay?"}
{2: 'Vera', 3: 'Who cares about them? We have our own mission.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: "Yeah, but you and that Commandant... Wazzat-face? 【kuroname】? Ain't ya drummed up about 'em?"}
{2: 'Vera', 3: "Say one more word. I'll cut your head off, bring it back to Babylonia, and sew it on a service robot.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: 'Fiiiiine fine... Guess we just do our job as usual.'}
